webpackJsonp([75895805060978],{1389:function(e,a){e.exports={data:{site:{siteMetadata:{title:"女王控的博客",description:'前端工程师，黑猫女王控，欢迎勾搭，技术相关<a href="https://github.com/towavephone" target="_blank">@towavephone</a>，QQ闲聊<a href="tencent://AddContact/?fromId=45&fromSubId=1&subcmd=all&uin=634407147&website=www.oicqzone.com">@towave</a>，bili关注<a href="https://space.bilibili.com/11507708#/" target="_blank">@towave</a>',siteUrl:"https://blog.towavephone.com"}}},pathContext:{posts:[{excerpt:"水平居中设置-行内元素 如果被设置元素为文本、图片等行内元素时，水平居中是通过给父元素设置  text-align:center  来实现的。 水平居中设置-定宽块状元素 满足定宽和块状两个条件的元素是可以通过设置 左右 margin 值为 auto 来实现居中的。 水平居中总结-不定宽块状元素方法 加入  table  标签 改变块级元素的 display 为 inline 类型（设置为 行内元素 显示），然后使用 text-align:center…",html:'<h1 id="水平居中设置-行内元素"><a href="#%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3%E5%B1%85%E4%B8%AD%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE-%E8%A1%8C%E5%86%85%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0" aria-hidden="true" class="anchor"><svg aria-hidden="true" height="16" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"></path></svg></a>水平居中设置-行内元素</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>如果被设置元素为文本、图片等行内元素时，水平居中是通过给父元素设置 <code>text-align:center</code> 来实现的。</li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n<h1 id="水平居中设置-定宽块状元素"><a href="#%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3%E5%B1%85%E4%B8%AD%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE-%E5%AE%9A%E5%AE%BD%E5%9D%97%E7%8A%B6%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0" aria-hidden="true" class="anchor"><svg aria-hidden="true" height="16" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"></path></svg></a>水平居中设置-定宽块状元素</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>满足定宽和块状两个条件的元素是可以通过设置<code>左右 margin</code>值为<code>auto</code>来实现居中的。</li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n<h1 id="水平居中总结-不定宽块状元素方法"><a href="#%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3%E5%B1%85%E4%B8%AD%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93-%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%9A%E5%AE%BD%E5%9D%97%E7%8A%B6%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95" aria-hidden="true" class="anchor"><svg aria-hidden="true" height="16" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"></path></svg></a>水平居中总结-不定宽块状元素方法</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>加入 <code>table</code> 标签</li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n<div\n              class="gatsby-code-button-container"\n              data-toaster-id="86690377081929480000"\n              data-toaster-class="gatsby-code-button-toaster"\n              data-toaster-text-class="gatsby-code-button-toaster-text"\n              data-toaster-text="复制成功"\n              data-toaster-duration="3500"\n              onClick="copyToClipboard(` {\n  display: table;\n  margin: 0 auto;\n}`, `86690377081929480000`)"\n            >\n              <div\n                class="gatsby-code-button"\n                \n              >\n                css 复制代码\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class="gatsby-highlight" data-language="css"><pre style="counter-reset: linenumber NaN" class="language-css line-numbers"><code class="language-css"> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>\n  <span class="token property">display</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> table<span class="token punctuation">;</span>\n  <span class="token property">margin</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> 0 auto<span class="token punctuation">;</span>\n<span class="token punctuation">}</span></code><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows" style="white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>改变块级元素的<code>display</code>为<code>inline</code>类型（设置为<code>行内元素</code>显示），然后使用<code>text-align:center</code>来实现居中效果</li>\n<li>通过给父元素设置<code>float</code>，然后给父元素设置<code>position:relative</code>和<code>left:50%</code>，子元素设置 <code>position:relative</code>和<code>left: -50%</code>来实现水平居中。</li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n<h1 id="垂直居中-父元素高度确定的单行文本"><a href="#%E5%9E%82%E7%9B%B4%E5%B1%85%E4%B8%AD-%E7%88%B6%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%E9%AB%98%E5%BA%A6%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%95%E8%A1%8C%E6%96%87%E6%9C%AC" aria-hidden="true" class="anchor"><svg aria-hidden="true" height="16" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"></path></svg></a>垂直居中-父元素高度确定的单行文本</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>通过设置父元素的<code>height</code>和<code>line-height</code>高度一致来实现的。(<code>height</code>: 该元素的高度，<code>line-height</code>: 顾名思义，行高（行间距），指在文本中，行与行之间的基线间的距离 )。</li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n<h1 id="垂直居中-父元素高度确定的多行文本"><a href="#%E5%9E%82%E7%9B%B4%E5%B1%85%E4%B8%AD-%E7%88%B6%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%E9%AB%98%E5%BA%A6%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%9A%E8%A1%8C%E6%96%87%E6%9C%AC" aria-hidden="true" class="anchor"><svg aria-hidden="true" height="16" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"></path></svg></a>垂直居中-父元素高度确定的多行文本</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>使用插入<code>table</code>(包括<code>tbody、tr、td</code>)标签，同时设置 <code>vertical-align：middle</code>。</li>\n<li>或者采用以下样式</li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n<div\n              class="gatsby-code-button-container"\n              data-toaster-id="30561556459339180000"\n              data-toaster-class="gatsby-code-button-toaster"\n              data-toaster-text-class="gatsby-code-button-toaster-text"\n              data-toaster-text="复制成功"\n              data-toaster-duration="3500"\n              onClick="copyToClipboard(` {\n  display: table-cell;\n  vertical-align: middle;\n}`, `30561556459339180000`)"\n            >\n              <div\n                class="gatsby-code-button"\n                \n              >\n                css 复制代码\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class="gatsby-highlight" data-language="css"><pre style="counter-reset: linenumber NaN" class="language-css line-numbers"><code class="language-css"> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>\n  <span class="token property">display</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> table-cell<span class="token punctuation">;</span>\n  <span class="token property">vertical-align</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> middle<span class="token punctuation">;</span>\n<span class="token punctuation">}</span></code><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows" style="white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h1 id="隐性改变-display-类型"><a href="#%E9%9A%90%E6%80%A7%E6%94%B9%E5%8F%98-display-%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B" aria-hidden="true" class="anchor"><svg aria-hidden="true" height="16" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"></path></svg></a>隐性改变 display 类型</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li><code>position : absolute </code></li>\n<li><code>float : left 或 float:right </code></li>\n<li>只要<code>html</code>代码中出现以上两句之一，元素的<code>display</code>显示类型就会自动变为以 <code>display:inline-block</code>（块状元素）的方式显示，当然就可以设置元素的 <code>width</code> 和 <code>height</code> 了，且默认宽度不占满父元素。</li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>',id:"/github/workspace/blog/CSS居中/index.md absPath of file >>> MarkdownRemark",timeToRead:2,frontmatter:{date:"2017-11-20 23:01:05",path:"/css-center/",tags:"前端, CSS, 居中",title:"CSS居中设置",draft:null}}],length:1,tag:"居中",pagesSum:1,page:1}}}});